Description: WOTCH supporters are the reason scheduled logging in coupe 'Blue Vein' were suspended until an extensive survey had been conducted by VicForests. They lobbied Lily DÕAmbrosio until the department was pressured to defer logging until a survey was conducted. This area of ancient Mountain Ash forest is within gliding distance of one of the Central Highlands biggest tourist attractions, the Ada tree. With 8 Leadbeater's Possum colonies sighted within 1km of this coupe, it is a major hotspot and a key stronghold for the survival of our Faunal Emblem.
